// AS3 linkage class `ScreenLanguage` is the openfl-swf generated library symbol `Screen_language` (the SWF symbol's
// library name was snake/lowerCamel; openfl names the class from it, not the AS3 linkage). Alias the
// two so `new ScreenLanguage()` constructs the real clip (with its named child instances), not an empty stub.
typedef ScreenLanguage = Screen_language;
